<p>This theme was created on top of <a href="https://scotte.github.io">Jekyll Clean theme</a> by Scotte.</p>

<p>This theme uses some parts of Twitter Bootstrap, which allows it looks nice on a mobile devices using a collapsable nav bar and hiding the sidebar.</p>

